"{\"uid\": \"cbsnews.com-news-paris-olympics-organizers-apologize-last-supper-tableau-religious-conservatives\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Watch CBS News  Updated on:  July 29, 2024 / 8:59 AM EDT/ CBS/AP  The organizers behind theParis Olympicsapologized to anyone who was offended by a tableau that evoked Leonardo da Vinci's \\\"The Last Supper\\\" during Friday's opening ceremony and provoked outrage by religious conservatives around the world.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 61, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS\", \"score\": 0.9999998332823591, \"rank\": 6.64525419487873e-08, \"text\": \"CBS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS\"}, {\"begin\": 168, \"end\": 185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8210131540474673e-23, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The organizers, however, defended the concept behind it.\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 361, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Da Vinci's painting depicts the moment when Jesus Christ declared that an apostle would betray him.\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 462, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 363, \"end\": 371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.36084010517945e-36, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 407, \"end\": 419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999990085930589, \"rank\": 9.914079212236808e-07, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thescene during Friday's ceremonyon the Debilly Bridge featured DJ and producer Barbara Butch - an LGBTQ+ icon who calls herself a \\\"love activist.\\\"\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Butch was wearing a silver headdress that looked like a halo as she got the party going on a footbridge across the Seine.\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 726, \"end\": 731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999890861, \"rank\": 1.0860781976858752e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Drag artists, dancers and others flanked Butch on both sides.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As CBS News correspondent Elaine Cobbe reports, the specific part of the ceremony that caused the offense was, in fact, a scene depicting Dionysus, the Greek god of wine.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9999999999399733, \"rank\": 5.989471989249326e-11, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}, {\"begin\": 822, \"end\": 828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elaine_Benes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.287041229105806e-20, \"text\": \"Elaine\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elaine_Benes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elaine_Benes\"}, {\"begin\": 934, \"end\": 942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1049757853203846e-23, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}, {\"begin\": 948, \"end\": 953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"score\": 0.892439531522303, \"rank\": 0.1199546809630054, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was reportedly based onThe Feast of the Gods,a 17th century painting by Dutch artist Jan Harmensz van Biljert that hangs in the Magnin Museum, in Dijon, eastern France.\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1042, \"end\": 1047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.9978648150057562, \"rank\": 0.0019464220660973608, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mus\\u00e9e_Magnin\", \"score\": 0.9999999944443516, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Magnin Museum\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mus\\u00e9e_Magnin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mus\\u00e9e_Magnin\"}, {\"begin\": 1116, \"end\": 1121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dijon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.73547777725689e-18, \"text\": \"Dijon\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dijon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dijon\"}, {\"begin\": 1131, \"end\": 1137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.995133809497358, \"rank\": 0.004711314041725426, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The painting depicts an assembly of Greek gods on Mount Olympus for a banquet to celebrate the marriage of Thetis and Peleus.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"score\": 0.984210305807712, \"rank\": 0.016043008388504528, \"text\": \"Greek gods\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}, {\"begin\": 1189, \"end\": 1202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8418259229462084e-24, \"text\": \"Mount Olympus\", \"types\": [\"Q8502\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The figure seated at the table in the center has a halo of light behind his head.\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thomas Jolly, the opening ceremony director, insisted in an interview with France's BFMTV that \\\"The Last Supper\\\" was not the inspiration behind the scene, explaining that \\\"Dionysus arrives at the table because he is the Greek God of celebration,\\\" adding that the particular sequence was entitled \\\"festivity.\\\"\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1348, \"end\": 1354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9999994576384431, \"rank\": 5.420561523764715e-07, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}, {\"begin\": 1423, \"end\": 1429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.995133809497358, \"rank\": 0.004711314041725426, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1432, \"end\": 1437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BFMTV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}, {\"begin\": 1520, \"end\": 1528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1049757853203846e-23, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}, {\"begin\": 1568, \"end\": 1573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"score\": 0.892439531522303, \"rank\": 0.1199546809630054, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The idea was to create a big pagan party in link with the God of Mount Olympus - and you will never find in me, or in my work, any desire of mocking anyone,\\\" Jolly said.\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"interpretation of the Greek God Dionysus makes us aware of the absurdity of violence between human beings,\\\" apost on the official social mediaaccount of the Olympic Games said by way of explanation.\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 2033, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1857, \"end\": 1862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"score\": 0.892439531522303, \"rank\": 0.1199546809630054, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}, {\"begin\": 1867, \"end\": 1875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1049757853203846e-23, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But religious conservatives from around the world decried the segment, with the French Catholic Church's conference of bishops deploring \\\"scenes of derision\\\" that they said made a mockery of Christianity - a sentiment echoed by Russian Foreign Ministry spokesperson Maria Zakharova.\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2115, \"end\": 2137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French Catholic Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church_in_France\"}, {\"begin\": 2122, \"end\": 2137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999989013304, \"rank\": 8.447380294478347e-10, \"text\": \"Catholic Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 2226, \"end\": 2238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9924005250793171, \"rank\": 0.0076575658790670655, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 2263, \"end\": 2287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\", \"score\": 0.999999999875854, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Russian Foreign Ministry\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\"}, {\"begin\": 2301, \"end\": 2316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Zakharova\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maria Zakharova\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Zakharova\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Zakharova\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Anglican Communion in Egypt expressed its \\\"deep regret\\\" Sunday, saying the ceremony could cause the IOC to \\\"lose its distinctive sporting identity and its humanitarian message.\\\"\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2322, \"end\": 2340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anglican_Communion\", \"score\": 0.9987047021242742, \"rank\": 0.0012969778484228495, \"text\": \"Anglican Communion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anglican_Communion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anglican_Communion\"}, {\"begin\": 2344, \"end\": 2349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"score\": 0.9873388176827678, \"rank\": 0.012822236831138062, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\"}, {\"begin\": 2422, \"end\": 2425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.65251417879467e-20, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prominent French far-right politician Marion Mar\\u00e9chal denounced the performance on social media.\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2511, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_far-right_movements_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French far-right\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_far-right_movements_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_far-right_movements_in_France\"}, {\"begin\": 2539, \"end\": 2554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marion_Mar\\u00e9chal\", \"score\": 0.9999998162447978, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marion Mar\\u00e9chal\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marion_Mar\\u00e9chal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marion_Mar\\u00e9chal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To all the Christians of the world who are watching the Paris 2024 ceremony and felt insulted by this drag queen parody of the Last Supper, know that it is not France that is speaking but a left-wing minority ready for any provocation,\\\" she posted on the social platform X, a sentiment that was echoed by religious conservatives internationally.\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2611, \"end\": 2621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9196745312546795, \"rank\": 0.06966154511050827, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 2656, \"end\": 2666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2042580661229345e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2760, \"end\": 2766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.995133809497358, \"rank\": 0.004711314041725426, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Romania, controversial social media influencer Andrew Tate and his brother Tristan Tate were part of a protest against the Olympics next to the French embassy in Bucharest on Sunday.\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 3132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3004, \"end\": 3008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"score\": 0.9998653723887356, \"rank\": 0.00013405481841296423, \"text\": \"Tate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\"}, {\"begin\": 3025, \"end\": 3032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"score\": 0.9999999989104253, \"rank\": 1.0897011571231598e-09, \"text\": \"Tristan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\"}, {\"begin\": 3033, \"end\": 3037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"score\": 0.9998653723887356, \"rank\": 0.00013405481841296423, \"text\": \"Tate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\"}, {\"begin\": 3094, \"end\": 3100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9901115954982238, \"rank\": 0.008584807068927777, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Tate brothers criticized the Olympic Games for mocking Christianity during the opening ceremony and called on athletes to boycott.\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3137, \"end\": 3141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"score\": 0.9998653723887356, \"rank\": 0.00013405481841296423, \"text\": \"Tate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\"}, {\"begin\": 3192, \"end\": 3204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9924005250793171, \"rank\": 0.0076575658790670655, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andrew Tate is awaiting trial in Romaniaon charges of allegedly forming an organized crime group, human trafficking and rape.\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3276, \"end\": 3280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"score\": 0.9998653723887356, \"rank\": 0.00013405481841296423, \"text\": \"Tate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tate\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony's artistic director Thomas Jolly distanced his scene from any \\\"Last Supper\\\" parallels after the ceremony, saying it was meant to celebrate diversity and pay tribute to feasting and French gastronomy.\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3429, \"end\": 3435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9999994576384431, \"rank\": 5.420561523764715e-07, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}, {\"begin\": 3590, \"end\": 3596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9901115954982238, \"rank\": 0.008584807068927777, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 spokesperson Anne Descamps was asked about the outcry during an International Olympic Committee news conference on Sunday.\", \"from\": 3609, \"to\": 3742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3609, \"end\": 3619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2042580661229345e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3638, \"end\": 3646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}, {\"begin\": 3684, \"end\": 3715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group.\", \"from\": 3744, \"to\": 3824, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the contrary, I think (with) Thomas Jolly, we really did try to celebrate community tolerance,\\\" Descamps said.\", \"from\": 3825, \"to\": 3938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3924, \"end\": 3932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking at the result of the polls that we shared, we believe that this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 3939, \"to\": 4034, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offense we are, of course, really, really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 4035, \"to\": 4109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jolly explained his intentions to The Associated Press after the ceremony.\", \"from\": 4111, \"to\": 4185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4149, \"end\": 4165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.9758031530190542, \"rank\": 0.024796852629611014, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My wish is not to be subversive, nor to mock or to shock,\\\" Jolly said.\", \"from\": 4187, \"to\": 4258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Most of all, I wanted to send a message of love, a message of inclusion and not at all to divide.\\\"\", \"from\": 4259, \"to\": 4358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2024 CBS Interactive Inc. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 4360, \"to\": 4408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4367, \"end\": 4387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CBS Interactive Inc.\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This material may not be published, broadcast, rewritten, or redistributed.\", \"from\": 4409, \"to\": 4484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Associated Press contributed to this report.\", \"from\": 4485, \"to\": 4533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4489, \"end\": 4505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.9758031530190542, \"rank\": 0.024796852629611014, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(02:27)  Copyright \\u00a92025 CBS Interactive Inc. All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 4535, \"to\": 4601, \"entities\": []}]}"